extendedInfo.description: With this horoscope application you'll have access to: - daily horoscope for all 12 zodiac signs- daily power numbers- daily predictions for: wellness, intellect, love, emotions, intuition, creativity, work and money.- find out who was born on the same day- horoscopes for previous and next daysIf you encounter any bugs/errors while using this application please contact us at: contact@dailyhoroscopes.netFind your western astrology zodiac sign:Aquarius (January 20 - February 18)Pisces (February 19 - March 20)Aries (March 21 - April 20)Taurus (April 21 - May 20)Gemini (May 21 - June 21)Cancer (June 22 - July 22)Leo (July 23 - August 23)Virgo (August 24 - September 22)Libra (September 23 - October 22)Scorpio (October 23 - November 21)Sagittarius (November 22 - December 21)Capricorn (December 22 - January 19)
